## Design Decisions Made

### 1. Visual Philosophy
- **Dark mode first** (Linear-inspired)
- **Islands UI pattern** (JetBrains Fleet-inspired)
- **Density with clarity** - enterprise-grade, not amateur

### 2. Primary Feature
- **Sandbox Mode** for what-if scenarios
- Directly addresses RFQ pain point #7: "No predictive simulations"

### 3. Implementation Approach
- **4-phase Storybook workflow**
- Each phase requires approval before proceeding
- Quality gates at each phase

### 4. Technology Stack
- Astro.js 4.x (static generation)
- deck.gl 9.x (WebGL visualization)
- XState 5.x (state machines)
- Tailwind CSS (styling)
- RBush (spatial indexing)

